  &lt;h1 class=&#34;my-4 font-normal text-center leading-tight&#34;&gt;
    Comparison of Mapbox GL JS vs D3.js
  &lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/section&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;flex h-64 mb-8&#34;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;w-1/2&#34;&gt;
